{"year":"2025","session":"2","grade":"Pre-1","qno":9,"question":"The store clerk told me my coupon was _____, so it could no longer be used. It had expired two months earlier.","translation":"店員は私のクーポンは無効だと言った。もう使えなかった。2か月前に期限切れになっていた。","choices":["acute","rash","invalid","imminent"],"answer":3,"explanation":"expired, could no longer be used がヒント。invalid = 無効な。","choice_notes":["acute=深刻な、鋭い","rash=軽率な、発疹","invalid=無効な","imminent=差し迫った"],"synonyms":"void, expired, not valid"},
