{"year":"2025","session":"2","grade":"Pre-1","qno":12,"question":"Although Jeffrey claimed it was an accident, Gretchen believed that he _____ knocked her books to the floor in order to make her angry.","translation":"ジェフリーは事故だったと主張したが、グレッチェンは彼女を怒らせるためにわざと本を床に落としたと信じていた。","choices":["greedily","obediently","intentionally","thoroughly"],"answer":3,"explanation":"in order to make her angry が目的を示す。intentionally = 意図的に。","choice_notes":["greedily=貪欲に","obediently=従順に","intentionally=意図的に","thoroughly=徹底的に"],"synonyms":"deliberately, purposely, on purpose"},
